---

<section id="servicios" class="py-24 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <span class="inline-block text-emerald-400 text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-4 border border-emerald-500/30 bg-emerald-500/10 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full">
        Lo que hacemos
      </span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight">Nuestros servicios</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-400 mt-4 max-w-xl mx-auto">Soluciones concretas para los desafíos reales de tu día a día.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Cards -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">

      <!-- Tarjeta 1: Gestión Comercial -->
      <div class="group flex flex-col p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/40 hover:border-emerald-500/50 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:bg-slate-900/70 transition-all duration-300 cursor-default">
        <div class="mb-6 w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/20 text-emerald-400 group-hover:bg-emerald-500/20 transition-colors duration-300">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M3 9l1-6h16l1 6"/>
            <path d="M3 9a2 2 0 0 0 2 2 2 2 0 0 0 2-2 2 2 0 0 0 2 2 2 2 0 0 0 2-2 2 2 0 0 0 2 2 2 2 0 0 0 2-2"/>
            <path d="M5 11v8a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h4v-5h4v5h4a1 1 0 0 0 1-1v-8"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-white">Gestión Comercial</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 flex-1">Controlá tu stock, registrá ventas y llevá las cuentas corrientes de tus clientes desde un solo lugar, sin complicaciones.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="text-xs text-emerald-400/80 bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/20 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Stock</span>
          <span class="text-xs text-emerald-400/80 bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/20 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Ventas</span>
          <span class="text-xs text-emerald-400/80 bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/20 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Cuentas corrientes</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Tarjeta 2: Software a Medida -->
      <div class="group flex flex-col p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/40 hover:border-emerald-500/50 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:bg-slate-900/70 transition-all duration-300 cursor-default">
        <div class="mb-6 w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/20 text-emerald-400 group-hover:bg-emerald-500/20 transition-colors duration-300">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/>
            <path d="M16 7V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v2"/>
            <line x1="12" y1="12" x2="12" y2="12.01"/>
            <path d="M2 12h20"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-white">Software a Medida</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 flex-1">Herramientas diseñadas específicamente para tu actividad profesional. Nos adaptamos a tu forma de trabajar, no al revés.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="text-xs text-emerald-400/80 bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/20 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Profesionales</span>
          <span class="text-xs text-emerald-400/80 bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/20 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Personalizado</span>
          <span class="text-xs text-emerald-400/80 bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/20 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Eficiencia</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Tarjeta 3: Soluciones para el Agro -->
      <div class="group flex flex-col p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/40 hover:border-emerald-500/50 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:bg-slate-900/70 transition-all duration-300 cursor-default">
        <div class="mb-6 w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/20 text-emerald-400 group-hover:bg-emerald-500/20 transition-colors duration-300">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M11 20A7 7 0 0 1 9.8 6.1C15.5 5 17 4.5 19 2c1 2 2 4.2 2 7 0 6.5-4.8 11-10 11z"/>
            <path d="M2 21c0-3 1.85-5.36 5.08-6C9.5 14.52 12 13 13 12"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-white">Soluciones para el Agro</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 flex-1">Llevá el control ganadero y el seguimiento de tu producción desde el celular, estés donde estés en el campo.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="text-xs text-emerald-400/80 bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/20 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Ganadería</span>
          <span class="text-xs text-emerald-400/80 bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/20 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Producción</span>
          <span class="text-xs text-emerald-400/80 bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/20 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Móvil</span>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
